data.title: Cerberus 420
data.meta_description: The Cerberus is a highly accurate, fully integrated; combination metal detection packaging inspection and check-weighing system specifically designed for High Care food production environments. The Cerberus is employed to check for potential metal contaminants, inspect the label and verify the weigh
